            "body": "Just read the design posted on YARN-1040. In the next iteration, can we please include details on the kinds of compatibility we preserve through this work and how? I have other more specific comments on the design, but I should probably wait for an updated design doc. \n\nIs this JIRA only for application upgrades? Does it also cater to the general case of decoupling allocations and containers/processes? Should YARN-1040 be closed as a duplicate of this? \n\n",
